tip.text: To order from this restaurant, show them this text, trust me: 볶음 우동 하나, 구운 연어 하나, 타구야기 하나 주세요. 그리고 미수수프 좀 주세요^^ 수하일 친구.
실시한 입? Have a Quiche 키쉬. super delicious, and it takes 20 minutes to make.
Drip coffee is rich. Americano is delicious. Latte is colorful. English muffin is lovely. The owner is awesome.
they have sea view low floor and high floor. The low floor (3rd floor) has a side where the view is actually blocked by their other building as in the picture. Confirm upon check-in.

tip.text: The light is dim because the building is old, I went to 2nd floor and searched for the Mosque for a while. 이 빌딩은 올드니까 빛은 어스레합니다. 2층에 갔을때 모스크를 찾았읍니다.

Outside the building, you won't see a sign of the Masjid at all. You will see the name of the building 동호상가. Go to the 2nd floor and search around until seeing the door in the picture. Friendly folks.
